<li><strong>High business value</strong> (pages that drive leads or revenue)</li>
<li><strong>Topic alignment</strong> (pages covering questions users ask AI engines)</li>
</ol>
<p>Pages with existing rankings convert easiest for GEO. They already have authority signals AI engines recognize.</p>
